---

---

<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <!-- Ambient glow -->
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-greeting reveal">
      <span class="greeting-line"></span>
      <span class="greeting-text">안녕하세요</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="hero-name reveal reveal-delay-1">
      김지훈<span class="dot">.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-role reveal reveal-delay-2">
      Frontend Developer
    </p>

    <p class="hero-desc reveal reveal-delay-3">
      사용자 경험을 중심으로 생각하는 프론트엔드 개발자입니다.<br />
      깔끔한 코드와 섬세한 인터랙션으로 가치를 만들어갑니다.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-cta reveal reveal-delay-4">
      <a href="#projects" class="btn-primary">
        프로젝트 보기
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
          <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#about" class="btn-ghost">About Me</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="scroll-indicator reveal reveal-delay-4">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 120px 24px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── Ambient background glow ── */
  .hero-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 700px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at center,
      rgba(232, 196, 104, 0.04) 0%,
      rgba(232, 196, 104, 0.015) 40%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: glowPulse 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  @keyframes glowPulse {
    0% { opacity: 0.6; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.08); }
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-greeting {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .greeting-line {
    display: block;
    width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent-gold);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .greeting-text {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 10vw, 96px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .dot {
    color: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  .hero-role {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 24px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 44px;
  }

  /* ── CTA Buttons ── */
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bg-primary);
    background: var(--accent-gold);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition:
      transform 0.25s var(--ease-out-expo),
      box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(232, 196, 104, 0.2);
  }

  .btn-primary svg {
    transition: transform 0.25s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition:
      color 0.25s,
      border-color 0.25s,
      transform 0.25s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-color: var(--text-muted);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* ── Scroll indicator ── */
  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent-gold), transparent);
    animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scrollPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scaleY(0.6); transform-origin: top; }
    50% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scaleY(1); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 100px 20px 60px;
    }
    .hero-desc br {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
